# Data — most derived artifacts ignored. Two exceptions:
#   - data/results/ (intentionally tracked: per-race JSONs from the workflow)
#   - data/processed/all_races.parquet (committed seed so CI doesn't have to
#     backfill 2019-2025 from FastF1 every time, which trips Ergast's
#     500 calls/hour rate limit on shared GitHub runner IPs)
data/raw/
data/processed/
!data/processed/all_races.parquet

